The SMART system also provides a set a corpora, queries and reference rankings, taken from different subjects, notably
<list>
<entry level="1" type="bullet">

 ADI: publications from information science reviews <weblink xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="ftp://ftp.cs.cornell.edu/pub/smart/adi">
ftp://ftp.cs.cornell.edu/pub/smart/adi</weblink></entry>
<entry level="1" type="bullet">

 CACM: computer science <weblink xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="ftp://ftp.cs.cornell.edu/pub/smart/cacm">
ftp://ftp.cs.cornell.edu/pub/smart/cacm</weblink></entry>
<entry level="1" type="bullet">

 Cranfield collection : publications from  aeronautic reviews <weblink xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="ftp://ftp.cs.cornell.edu/pub/smart/cran/">
ftp://ftp.cs.cornell.edu/pub/smart/cran/</weblink></entry>
<entry level="1" type="bullet">

